{"tid":1540512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求。缺一不可！！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:53:58.000Z","uid":195846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"508281d31b1ee84e58f48d66f4f03ced309f2de5","tid":1540512,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭講咩會動議徹回？ 先唔好話是否=徹回<br />\n<br />\n佢今次明顯係中共一貫作風<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉一派，打一派</span></span>完全睇唔到有任何誠意<br />\n<br />\n好明顯係因為呢3個月一直想分割和理非及勇武，而加見事不可為就轉而想分割<strong>淺黃</strong>同廿<strong>黃</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，大家要知道今次運動點解政府用唔到拖字訣就係因為有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武</span>迫到政府要即刻回應 但大家都知政府既回應係咩 就係濫打濫捕 <br />\n<br />\n聽一聽梁天琦講過啲咩 2條片都係幾分鐘 唔阻你好多時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/36olyar0wHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F36olyar0wHE&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=b40aa384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/36olyar0wHE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GP1Tdqp8UxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGP1Tdqp8UxE&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=3ceecb8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GP1Tdqp8UxE</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">基本法承諾2017，2020雙普選</span></span>我地唔止呢樣權利比人剝削呀，我地連最基本<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">免受恐懼既權利都冇呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而加過左3個月1100幾人被捕8條人命3隻眼睛 而加話要溝通？佔中話要溝通，之後？<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔好聽少佢聲明最後一部分 係維護法治 嚴正執法呀<br />\n姐係繼續撐克警呀<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求分別係對應各種既問題<br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個長久既抗爭 但大家 做到幾多做幾多！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，不離不棄！<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"c2136918297eff000fe764b5b7fa27c690e19280","tid":1540512,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna